00:25:06.140 --> 00:25:08.090
with the community, and
to get the community

00:25:08.090 --> 00:25:10.370
to see the police as a
force that will help them,

00:25:10.370 --> 00:25:14.099
as opposed to just arrest them,
or enforce the laws on them.

00:25:14.099 --> 00:25:15.890
