up to an hour from your backup.

00:27:53.930 --> 00:27:55.490
So that also influences.

00:27:55.490 --> 00:27:58.295
And also just the rural
nature of a lot of the land.

00:27:58.295 --> 00:28:00.170
So I think one of the
challenges in coming up

00:28:00.170 --> 00:28:02.150
with good solutions
to reform policing

00:28:02.150 --> 00:28:03.920
is to make it scalable.

00:28:03.920 --> 00:28:05.940
And so when--

00:28:05.940 --> 00:28:07.190
