00:28:07.190 --> 00:28:10.360
When Tukwila hears what
Seattle's doing, they're like,

00:28:10.360 --> 00:28:12.740
ugh, you know, we can't do it.

00:28:12.740 --> 00:28:14.390
So thinking in
those terms as well,

00:28:14.390 --> 00:28:17.096
what's possible
within what you have.

